{
  "stem": "4226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's hobby was-- he, he did woodworking, his hobby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm doing it, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the last three years during the Second World War, he actually leased the building, which had the cheder and the livestock and the [INAUDIBLE] machinery.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He leased it to a Turkish company, who employed Ukrainian-Russian people from Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they produced dried prunes from fresh-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what you call that prunes-- Angelina.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Angelina plums, the blue ones, which you eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they even made delicacies, I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- after a day, it, it was put into, into this huge stove, which were in the ground, 2-meter-diameter pipes running in-- and above were a structure of timber, with trays in it and doors.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Each door had about five trays, and were five, five-- 3 times 5 vertically and all along, could have been about 25 feet each.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a lot of plums went in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those plums-- you, you could-- after a day, 24 hours, you could take the plums out, and squeeze the seed out through one end of it, and replace it with, with a walnut-- Wow.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with a walnut seed and keep drying it further.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I shouldn't have told you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is trade secrets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they, they kept it till, till the-- we were deported from that place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was seasonal because they only used it for about three months in a year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in the whole area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People came with the plums in horse-drawn carriages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were selling them to this company.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They went, went onto the scale with the livestock, with the carriage, and then when empty.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
